The Al Ansaar Cancer Support Group held its monthly support meeting on 14 September at the Al Ansaar Hall in Overport. Patients, caregivers and family members were treated to a wonderful and an inspiring talk by Safiya Kazi, a life coach.  The group will also host their annual Chai Day on 19 October at 9am at the Al Ansaar Hall. The  Cancer Support Group is open to all female patients, caregivers and family members.For more information, Luthfia Kajee can be contacted on 083 291 1786.